@startuml
title System Context Diagram for Intelligent Document Digitization Platform

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #7A7A7A
skinparam ArrowFontColor #5F5F5F
skinparam TitleFontColor black

skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 6
  BorderColor transparent
  FontColor white
  FontSize 15
}

rectangle "«person»\n\nEnterprise User\n\nEmployees who upload,\nsearch, review, and manage\nbusiness documents" as EnterpriseUser #0E4B8F

rectangle "«person»\n\nSystem Administrator\n\nIT staff responsible for platform\nadministration, monitoring,\nconfiguration, and access control" as SysAdmin #0E4B8F

rectangle "«external_system»\n\nClient Systems\n\nEnterprise applications that integrate\nwith the platform through APIs" as ClientSystems #9A9A9A

rectangle "«system»\n\nIntelligent Document Digitization and\nManagement Platform\n\nDigitizes, extracts, classifies,\nindexes, archives, and manages\nenterprise documents" as IDDMP #1565C0

rectangle "«external_system»\n\nExternal Auth Service\n\nExternal identity provider used for\nauthentication and access control\n(optional)" as AuthService #9A9A9A

EnterpriseUser --> IDDMP : Uploads documents,\nsearches content,\nreviews extracted metadata
SysAdmin --> IDDMP : Configures platform services,\nmonitors processing pipelines
ClientSystems --> IDDMP : Submits documents and\nretrieves processing results\nthrough the platform API
IDDMP --> AuthService : Delegates user authentication\nand token validation (optional)

@enduml